column2: SELECT objid, nvote, p_el as elliptical, p_cw as spiralclock, p_acw as spiralanticlock, p_edge as edgeon, p_dk as dontknow, p_mg as merger into mydb.MyTable from ZooNoSpec WHERE objid = # SELECT ALL g.objid, zns.nvote, zns.p_el as elliptical, zns.p_cw as spiralclock, zns.p_acw as spiralanticlock, zns.p_edge as edgeon, zns.p_dk as dontknow, zns.p_mg as merger FROM Galaxy as G JOIN ZooNoSpec AS zns ON G.objid = zns.objid WHERE g.clean = # and zns.nvote > = # and zns.p_cw > #
